            "value": [
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/39410",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=rob",
                        "name": "rob",
                        "displayName": "Rob Allen",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "Looking at isValidPartial(), the correct patch is:\r\n\r\n{code}\r\nIndex: library\/Zend\/Form.php\r\n===================================================================\r\n--- library\/Zend\/Form.php\t(revision 21590)\r\n+++ library\/Zend\/Form.php\t(working copy)\r\n@@ -2031,7 +2031,9 @@\r\n         }\r\n \r\n         foreach ($this->getElements() as $key => $element) {\r\n-            $element->setTranslator($translator);\r\n+            if (null !== $translator) {\r\n+                $element->setTranslator($translator);\r\n+            }\r\n             if (!isset($data[$key])) {\r\n                 $valid = $element->isValid(null, $data) && $valid;\r\n             } else {\r\n{code}\r\n",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=rob",
                        "name": "rob",
                        "displayName": "Rob Allen",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2010-03-21T04:32:01.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2010-03-21T04:32:01.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/39412",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=rob",
                        "name": "rob",
                        "displayName": "Rob Allen",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "Fixed on trunk r21591. Fixed on release-1.10 branch r21593 (http:\/\/framework.zend.com\/code\/changelog\/Zend_Framework?cs=21593)",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=rob",
                        "name": "rob",
                        "displayName": "Rob Allen",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2010-03-21T04:39:57.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2010-03-21T04:39:57.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/39489",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=alab",
                        "name": "alab",
                        "displayName": "Christian Albrecht",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "Sorry, Rob, it seems to me you missed the point. Because when setting a translator on\r\nForm Level in addition to setting a translator on an Element, the Forms Translator will\r\nneverless overwrite the Elements Translator.\r\n\r\nWould you mind to have a look at [ZF-9364]?",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=alab",
                        "name": "alab",
                        "displayName": "Christian Albrecht",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2010-03-23T11:01:17.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2010-03-23T11:01:17.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/39490",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=alab",
                        "name": "alab",
                        "displayName": "Christian Albrecht",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "Duh, or did I? Is the Forms Translator supposed to be more mightful than the Translators on Element Level?",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=alab",
                        "name": "alab",
                        "displayName": "Christian Albrecht",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2010-03-23T11:11:50.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2010-03-23T11:11:50.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/39494",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=rob",
                        "name": "rob",
                        "displayName": "Rob Allen",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "Christian,\r\n\r\nYou're right in that if there is a forms level translator, it should override the element one. It has to be like that in order to preserve B\/C. \r\n\r\nThis issue is concerned with the case when you don't have a forms level one but do have an element level. Prior to this path, the element level was was removed even though there was no forms level translator to replace it.\r\n\r\nRegards,\r\n\r\nRob...",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=rob",
                        "name": "rob",
                        "displayName": "Rob Allen",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2010-03-23T12:57:04.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2010-03-23T12:57:04.000+0000"
                }
            ]
        }
